</code></pre> <h4 id=help> <a class=anchor href="#help"><span class=visuallyhidden>&#8211;help permalink</span></a><code>--help</code> </h4> <p>This flag (abbreviated <code>-h</code>) prints a summary of this&nbsp;documentation.</p> <pre class="highlight plaintext"><code>$ sass --help
Compile Sass to CSS.

Usage: sass &lt;input.scss&gt; [output.css]
       sass &lt;input.scss&gt;:&lt;output.css&gt; &lt;input/&gt;:&lt;output/&gt;

...
</code></pre> <h4 id=version> <a class=anchor href="#version"><span class=visuallyhidden>&#8211;version permalink</span></a><code>--version</code> </h4> <p>This flag prints the current version of&nbsp;Sass.</p> <pre class="highlight plaintext"><code>$ sass --version
1.24.4
